  <brief_title>OCT in Borderline Coronary Artery Lesions</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Safety and Efficacy of OCT in the Evaluation and Treatment of Angiographically Borderline Coronary Artery Lesions</official_title>
  <sponsors>
